  "texts": [
    "Note, this process would be repeated for each input word giving a unique positional encoding for each input word.",
    "decoder-only models (Vaswani et al., 2017; Radford et al., 2018 Radford et al.,, 2019;; Brown et al., 2020; Naveed et al., 2023).",
    "Multihead attention allows the LLM to perform parallel attention computations with different projections of the query, key, and value vectors.",
    "The outputs of these computations are then concatenated and projected again to produce the final output.",
    "It is this multihead attention that allows the model to attend to different aspects of the input or output data at different positions."
  ],
